/home/user has (desktop, video, music) is where all the user files are stored
this is for security, portability

/var/log,mail,spool,/    contains semi permanent 

/etc/password,ssh,skel,

/ect/ssh/
bin - user binaries
S bin - system binaries
lib - libraries
share - fonts/pics

